## Methodology & Process

### 5-Phase Process
1. **Discovery & Analysis** - Stakeholder mapping, technical landscape, content audit
2. **Documentation Creation** - Structure planning, content development, documentation-first approach
3. **Design & Presentation** - Visual design, content organization, responsive layouts
4. **Client Handoff** - Repository strategy, multi-audience handoff, training programs
5. **Quality Assurance** - 4-stage review process, testing protocols, client feedback

### Required Documentation Files
Always generate:
- README.md (static memory file)
- docs/theme-architecture.md
- docs/technical-user-guide.md
- docs/business-user-guide.md
- docs/data-guide.md
- docs/integrations.md
- docs/QUICK_REFERENCE.md

Conditional (when available):
- docs/performance.md
- docs/accessibility.md

## Tone & Style Guidelines

### Writing Style
- **Professional but clear** - No unnecessary formality
- **Pragmatic and confident** - Grounded logic, premium clarity
- **Direct but not cold** - Midwest-based digital transformation partner tone
- **Skimmable** - Use bullet points, headings, summaries
- **Precise** - Surgical suggestions, precise execution

### Documentation Standards
- Use clear formatting (headings, bullet points, summaries)
- Visual hierarchy matters
- Consistent terminology
- Progressive disclosure (start high-level, drill down)
- Use case-driven organization

### Code & Technical Writing
- Reference actual code when possible
- Include code examples with context
- Explain the "why" not just the "what"
- Document investigation patterns
- Preserve real error logs and test data

## Template System

### Core Components
- Dynamic header/footer via `component-loader.js`
- Enhanced TOC with scroll-based highlighting
- Mobile-responsive design
- Client customization placeholders

### Template Files
- `html-template.html` - Main template (index or doc page)
- `header-template.html` - Header component
- `footer-template.html` - Footer component
- `component-loader.js` - Dynamic loader
- `enhanced-toc/enhanced-toc.js` - Interactive TOC

