## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

- Forgetting to customize templates (copy header-template.html → header.html)
- Missing section IDs (Enhanced TOC requires matching IDs)
- Not testing component loading
- Technical jargon without business context
- Documenting without evidence (verify against actual code)
- Mixing temporary investigation work with permanent documentation
- Not updating README.md when structure changes
- Creating documentation that doesn't match actual implementation

